HEADWORD: Insociate
<hw>In*so"ci*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not associate;
without a companion; single; solitary; recluse.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>insociate</xex> virgin life.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

